        <property propertyId="38f94dd1-d5aa-41b8-b182-c0c42985d9dc" amount="2.68" unitId="7b75baf0-cbee-45e6-bf66-af119da06553">
          <name xml:lang="en">price</name>
          <unitName xml:lang="en">EUR2005</unitName>
          <comment xml:lang="en">Calculated value based on data from United Nations Commodity Trade Statistics Database (comtrade.un.org). UN comtrade category: 280410 Hydrogen. Year 2005. Using exchange rate of 1EURO = 1.209 USD. Average of price of import into 5 main markets (EU, US, JP, IN and CN). Cross reference; Literature (http://www.ttcorp.com/pdf/marketReport.pdf). The price of hydrogen, liquid is 5-10 USD/kg.</comment>
        </property>
